her two-fifths or three-fifths of the people polled said that <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON> was more conservative than <PERSON> Bush </PERSON>. That is n't a loss of focus, that's a loss of your eyeglasses,'' <PERSON> Simpson </PERSON> said. `` There is n't any way <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON> is going to pull that one off.''
